title: Shutdown Fullcast 40 for 40: The 2017 Camellia Bowl
description:
Peanut butter and jelly. Sea anemones and clownfish. The Civil Rights Movement and an unsponsored bowl in Montgomery that ESPN just runs on its own and you probably won't watch. These are all things that totally go together and you should never think otherwise, you jerk.
